                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.52/271b.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Special
                        Agent <persName type="to">Carothers</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-05-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 14, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The following telegram has been sent to American Consulate at Durango: [Telegram
                    to Consul Hamm, May 14, 1914.]</p>
                <p>We suggest that you take the matter up with Villa also.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
